name: Unidentified_Trandoshan_hunter_(Krystar)
content: A Trandoshan hunter was active during the Clone Wars, purchasing clone troopers that had been held prisoner by Regent Queb of the planet Krystar. Vishar Koss, a representative for the planet, learned of the compound where Queb held the troopers, and contacted Senator Padm√© Amidala of the Galactic Republic. The Republic undertook a mission to rescue the clones, and Queb and the Trandoshan were stopped by Jedi General Obi-Wan Kenobi.
